DecisionTableView is part of the Utah Decision Support Tools.

Author:
J. Michael Dean, M.D., M.B.A.

November 26, 2006 13:29 PM

University of Utah School of Medicine, Salt Lake City, Utah

Purpose of the class: List decisions for a specific patient in a table. The object is a selection listener in order to be informed about which patient has been selected by the user.
